   | HistoryPrev            | up,C-p          | history, moves backwards in |
   |                        |                 | the history.                |
   |------------------------+-----------------+-----------------------------|
   | Hold                   | =               | Places a package on hold.   |
   |------------------------+-----------------+-----------------------------|
